This harmonious combination of natural mango wood and strong iron creates a striking silhouette that is perfectly suited for any contemporary kitchen or dining space. The raw, rustic aesthetic of the Loko stool adds a touch of artisan charm and an element of organic sophistication to your interior design. Its substantial yet balanced construction makes it an ideal choice for adding both style and practical seating to your home. Whether placed in a modern kitchen as a breakfast bar stool, used as a distinctive accent piece in a living area, or even as a unique side table, the Loko stool is designed to be a focal point. Its versatility allows it to seamlessly integrate into various décor styles, from rustic farmhouse to modern industrial. Nkuku's commitment to ethical sourcing and artisanal quality is evident in every Loko stool, offering you a piece that is not only beautiful but also responsibly made. Experience the perfect fusion of organic materials, handcrafted detail, and enduring design with this exceptional stool.

products.title: Ferre Iron Sideboard - Industrial Black Metal, Black Fir Wood with Glass Doors & Lockable Castors
products.description: Ferre Iron Sideboard - Industrial Black Metal, Black Fir Wood with Glass Doors & Lockable Castors. This stunning sideboard from White Label Living seamlessly blends industrial style with a touch of rustic charm. The striking industrial black metal framework provides a robust and visually captivating foundation, creating a bold statement piece for any living space. This strong metal frame is perfectly complemented by the rich warmth of the black fir wood veneer, which adds depth and texture, softening the industrial aesthetic and creating a beautifully balanced contrast. The inclusion of glass doors is not just aesthetically pleasing; they showcase your cherished belongings, adding a personalized touch to your home. The glass panels themselves appear to be made of high-quality tempered glass offering both style and durability. You'll find it effortless to rearrange your storage layout thanks to the cleverly incorporated shelf, which runs the full width of the interior space. This allows for versatile storage options—perfect for crockery, books, linens, or any items you desire to keep organized yet readily accessible. Adding further practicality and design elements are the lockable castors. These high-quality castors not only ensure that the sideboard is easy to maneuver and reposition within your home but also contribute to the piece's stylish aesthetic, with their polished metallic finish complementing the existing design details. The ability to lock the castors will help to ensure the unit is sturdy and secure once positioned where desired, reducing any risk of accidental movements and maintaining the stability of your beautifully presented items. This well-designed unit includes four individual doors – two on each side, evenly spaced – providing an impressive amount of closed-door storage for those things you'd prefer to keep neatly hidden. These doors can provide private storage within each compartment whilst also concealing their contents behind the sophisticated look and function of the cabinet and metal frame. The sideboard has a substantial size that speaks volumes of both storage space and commanding presence. Given that it’s created from high-quality materials the structure of this wonderful sideboard is robust and has exceptional longevity for long-lasting, hassle-free usage. Whether placed in a dining room, living room, or hallway, the Ferre Iron Sideboard is certain to become a stylish centerpiece in your home adding both practical functionality and aesthetic appeal. With its careful blend of materials, versatile storage capabilities, and effortless maneuverability, the Ferre Iron Sideboard transcends the limitations of simple furniture and transcends to the next level. It’s much more than just storage, it's an investment in refined style and quality, seamlessly integrating practicality and elegance. The use of strong black industrial metal with a contrasting elegant warmth from the darker fir wood adds further dimensions to this exceptional design that’s guaranteed to enhance and brighten the most elegant living spaces in any setting.

products.description: Nkuku Anbu Mango Wood Upholstered Dining Chair Natural Introducing the Nkuku Anbu Mango Wood Upholstered Dining Chair in Natural, a truly exquisite and timeless piece designed to elevate your dining experience. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, this chair is an elegant addition to any dining space, exuding a classic and sophisticated aura. The robust frame is meticulously hand carved from solid mango wood, a sustainable and durable hardwood known for its beautiful grain patterns and natural warmth. This commitment to artisanal craftsmanship is further evident in the natural linen upholstery, which has also been stitched by hand, ensuring a unique and high-quality finish. The organic curves of the chair's design seamlessly blend with the understated simplicity of its legs, creating a harmonious and visually pleasing aesthetic. The beautifully light, natural finish of the mango wood complements the textured linen upholstery perfectly, resulting in a chair that is not just functional but a true statement piece. It will undoubtedly deserve pride of place around your dining table, fostering intimate meals and lively gatherings. Equally suited for a home office or study, this chair provides comfortable and stylish seating beneath your desk. To further enhance your living space and create a cohesive look, we invite you to explore the rest of the Anbu range, offering complementary pieces that embody the same commitment to quality and design. Additionally, discover more of our contemporary chairs to find the perfect match for your individual style and needs. This dining chair is more than just furniture; it is a testament to traditional craftsmanship and modern sensibility. The natural linen is soft to the touch, offering comfort and breathability during extended seating periods. The mango wood’s inherent strength ensures longevity and resilience, making this chair a wise investment for your home. Its versatility allows it to seamlessly integrate into various interior design schemes, from rustic farmhouse to minimalist modern. The hand-carved details on the frame, though subtle, add a touch of artisanal charm and uniqueness that mass-produced furniture simply cannot replicate. The carefully considered proportions and ergonomic design ensure that comfort is not sacrificed for style, making it a pleasure to sit in for both short meals and longer social occasions. The light finish of the mango wood accentuates the natural beauty of the wood grain, providing a warm and inviting feel to your dining area. The overall impression is one of understated luxury and enduring appeal.

Constructed from the finest solid oak and veneers, the bench boasts exceptional durability and a timeless appeal. The use of solid oak ensures the bench’s strength and longevity, resisting the wear and tear of daily use, while the veneers contribute to the beautiful grain patterns and rich color variations inherent in the wood. Handcrafted detailing is evident throughout the piece, reflecting a commitment to quality and meticulous craftsmanship. The bench's elegant profiles and smooth, rounded edges add a touch of understated luxury. Notice the distinctive tapered legs, a hallmark of Scandinavian design, which contribute to the bench's stability and its visually appealing silhouette. These tapered legs provide both structural integrity and a graceful visual balance. The smoothly rounded edges, not only aesthetically pleasing, also enhance safety and prevent sharp corners that could be a hazard, especially in households with children. The bench is remarkably versatile; its design makes it a striking standalone piece capable of adding warmth and character to a hallway or entryway, while its inherent functionality perfectly complements the Laholm dining table, creating a cohesive and stylish dining set. The rich, natural tone of the oak wood beautifully complements a wide range of decor styles, from modern minimalist interiors to more traditional settings, adapting effortlessly to various aesthetic preferences. The Laholm bench represents more than just seating; it is a testament to enduring craftsmanship and timeless design, promising years of both functionality and aesthetic pleasure within your home. The combination of solid oak and expertly applied veneers provides a visually stunning and structurally sound piece that is built to last. The choice of solid oak ensures not only durability but also contributes to a piece that ages beautifully, its natural patina deepening over time adding character and warmth to the piece, creating a heirloom-quality item that gets better with age. This is not simply a bench; it is an investment in enduring style and enduring quality that enhances the ambience and sophistication of your living space. Its smooth finish is inviting and durable, capable of handling the demands of everyday use. The timeless aesthetic guarantees it won't be replaced as trends evolve, making it a perfect blend of modern functionality with an elegant classic form that seamlessly integrates into your dining area or any other living space you chose.

The Vondel Outdoor Bistro Table from Zuiver is chic, sleek and available in a choice of three contemporary colours. Ideal for patios and smaller spaces, pull up a chair or two and watch the world go by. Part of the Vondel outdoor range, see below for details.

products.title: Woood Level Metal TV Cabinet- Honey Yellow or Sand - Honey Yellow
products.description: For media storage that makes a statement check out the Woood Level Metal TV Cabinet in Honey Yellow or Sand. This contemporary cabinet, from the collection of Dutch interior design brand WOOOD, contains several compartments behind four stylish doors so you can easily store accessories and media equipment out of sight. The addition of two openings in the back panel means that cords, cables and wires can be kept tidy and hidden from view. Made from powder coated iron this is a sturdy and practical addition to any home. With it’s interesting panel-effect and choice of two modern colours the Level is sure to create a warm and stylish atmosphere in your living space! See below for more of our media storage…

products.title: Extreme Lounging Teddy B-Poufe - Soft Grey
products.description: Like a big bear hug- the Extreme Lounging Teddy B-Pouf! Made from the cosiest most snuggly of fabrics, lightweight yet durable, this pouf is sure to be a favourite addition to lounges, nurseries or any room where you just want to be cosy. With a choice of five soft shades the Teddy B-Poufe is ideal as extra seating or when coupled with a Teddy B-Bag you have the ultimate in cute, feet-up relaxation! If you love it, why not take a peek below at more of our Extreme Lounging products?

products.title: Extreme Lounging Outdoor B-Box - Sea Blue
products.description: Put your feet up and enjoy the sunshine this Summer with our Extreme Lounging Outdoor B-Box. This sturdy little number is lightweight, durable and weatherproof and will add an extra dimension to your outdoor space. Designed to complement the Outdoor B-Bags in a wide range of striking colours but equally provides an informal seat for guests in your garden. Why not browse the range of complimentary outdoor products below?

products.title: Nordal Viva Black Wood Sideboard with Glass Doors
products.description: Create a personalised atmosphere in your home with the Nordal Viva Black Wood Sideboard with Glass Doors. This elegant cabinet features sleek black edges providing a stylish frame to showcase your favourite items inside. The warmth of the wood interior contrasts beautifully adding character and charm to the piece, whilst the combination of handy drawers and height adjustable shelves make this a real storage saviour. Versatile and functional, the low sideboard is ideal for any room in your home and provides the perfect opportunity to personalise your space. Add candlesticks, ornaments, photos or vases of flowers to tell your own style story! Why not see below for more of the Viva range and similar items?

products.title: Swyft Model 03 Corner Sofa with Ottoman in Velvet - Vine
products.description: Make up your own rules with the Swyft Model 03 Corner Sofa with Ottoman in Velvet. Your living room is your playground and with the Model 03 range you get to have fun and be in control! From 2 seats to 10, left or right hand corner and with or without an ottoman, the choice is yours. The modules are separate and don't lock together so you have the flexibility of movement and transformation of your space. Rubber feet create suction to stop the modules from moving once in place. The corner sofa with ottoman is a combination of one left arm, one right arm, two single, a corner module and an ottoman. Deep, squishy and the ultimate in comfort - this really is the bee's knees when it come to modern day lounging. Super comfort meets super flexible and available in a choice of 5 colours! Why not request a swatch box by emailing us at info@accessoriesforthehome.co.uk  Also available in linen.

products.title: Tom Rattan Rocking Chair - Black
products.description: * PLEASE NOTE THE NATURAL TOM IS CURRENTLY UNAVAILABLE UNTIL SPRING 2026 * Relax and recharge with the Tom Rattan Rocking Chair from the collection of Dutch brand WOOOD. Perfect for creating a little haven in your lounge, bedroom or nursery, this classic chair has the added bonus of a sturdy, metal rocking frame. As if this isn't enough, the beautifully weaved rattan has a waterproof coating meaning Tom is equally happy to be used outdoors in warmer months. Available in natural rattan or classic black, occasional seating doesn't get much better than this!

products.title: Muubs Bonbonniere Echo Storage Pot - Rust Grey
products.description: The Muubs Bonbonniere Echo Storage Pot has to be the most stylish place to hide your most treasured trinkets! The unique surface and rustic colours are created through a specific painting technique, after which the Bonbonniere is burned and glazed to achieve the very distinctive appearance. In addition to providing a place for small items, such as keys, coins and jewellery, you also gain a beautifully decorative piece. Perfect when combined with iron or wood pieces of furniture to create contrasts in both colour and material.

Finished in a classic matt coating, the Honey Yellow shade is designed to pop in any contemporary living space. Why not brighten up your home with the Exhibit? See below for the smaller version and for more of this funky range. Also see the co-ordinating Blanco Honey Yellow Circular Dining Table...
